title: Delta Force Land Warrior Demo* Remix*
description:
DFLW Demo V2

[img]http://dfzone.be/images/DFRLogo.jpg[/img]

After the fall of the original Delta Force Land Warrior Demo, a group of individuals from the DFLWD Community banded together to create this modified custom version of the Demo which contains objects and terrains from previous and future Novalogic Games.

Please note this is no longer hosted by Novalogic. This version is hosted by a 3rd party. 100% free,Open to the Public and anybody can host a server.
 The game is still as fun as its ever been and its great for anyone who doesn&#039;t have the money or a good computer. 
It takes up less computer resources, is smaller than 100 MB to download and less than 250 MB once installed. 

Seed and Enjoy  ;D
